request.description:
Creates a new agent. Use this endpoint to create an agent before starting conversations. The response will include the agentId.

Request body:
- agentType (optional): The type of agent to create. If not provided, defaults to GlobalAgent. Example: {"agentType": "GlobalAgent"}

body.raw:
{
  "agentId": "{{agentId}}",
  "message": "What is the population of that city?"
}

{
